sentence: In early trading on Wednesday, shares of International Business Machines ( IBM ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.5%.
Year to date, International Business Machines registers a 4.9% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is UnitedHealth Group ( UNH ), trading down 0.0%.
UnitedHealth Group is showing a gain of 15.7% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Home Depot ( HD ), trading up 0.1%, and Intel Corp ( INTC ), trading up 1.4% on the day.
